titles.title: Electing certain Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.
Electing certain Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

term.name: House Committee on Ways and Means

bill.summary: This resolution elects specified Members to the following House committees: (1) Representative Nanette Barragan of California to Natural Resources, and (2) Representative Cedric Richmond of Louisiana to Ways and Means.
